abstract: >-
  A reproducible pipeline for generating, testing, labeling, and analyzing bug
  types in LLM-generated Python code on HumanEval. The software produces failure
  signals, bug taxonomy labels, logic-error subtype labels, agreement analyses,
  tables, figures, and manuscript-ready artifacts.
keywords:
  - large language models
  - code generation
  - software bugs
  - empirical software engineering
  - reproducibility
